{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2967220/extras/Yan_Parasomnia_Title.gif?t=1720511283\" /><br><br>\u201cMama Wan has just passed. Mum had to leave work early today to prepare for the funeral. Brother and I will be taking the bus after school. It\u2019s been a while since we have gone back there.\u201c<br><br><strong>A Forlorn Homecoming</strong><br>Explore the decrepit apartments of Wallace Court as either Wan Zi Min or Wan Zi Han, a sister-brother duo with a formerly unknown heritage, as they are unwittingly dragged into thwarting a sinister disturbance so close to home.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2967220/extras/Multiplayer-Selection.gif?t=1720511283\" /><br><br><strong>A Trial of Two Wanderers</strong><br>Featuring the option for either a <strong>single-player</strong> experience or <strong>two-player co-op</strong>, you and a friend can journey into the spiritual realm together. <strong>Solve puzzles</strong>, <strong>ward off phantoms</strong>, and engage in bouts of sibling rivalry. After all, two heads are supposedly better than one.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2967220/extras/Yan_Parasomnia_Camera_Perspective.gif?t=1720511283\" /><br><br><strong>An Old-School Perspective</strong><br>Drawing inspiration from other classics of survival horror, experience the nostalgia when the genre was first being defined as you search through haunted remains and unravel dark mysteries. Confront the supernatural using modernised controls with classic gameplay.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2967220/extras/Yan_Parasomnia_Ghost.gif?t=1720511283\" /><br><br><strong>A Time When Spirits Walk the Earth</strong><br>Set during the late 20th century, when superstition and folklore were inseparable from everyday life, you will encounter various ghosts and spirits during your journey. While some would love to talk your young ears off, others may be less than pleased to meet you.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2967220/extras/Yan_Parasomnia_Kopitiam.gif?t=1720511283\" /><br><br><strong>A World to Explore</strong><br>From dilapidated apartment blocks (inspired by Southeast Asian structures) to other less-than-normal environments, you will traverse a number of varying landscapes as you attempt to piece together the unfolding truth. Keep your wits about you as the realms can be misleading.<br><br><strong>An Ending Driven by Choice</strong><br><strong>Every action you take, has a consequence.</strong> From spending time with a stray cat to assisting strange neighbours with equally strange requests, the ending of YAN\u9b47: PARASOMNIA is wholly and directly driven by your very actions. <strong>You choose your ending.</strong> Dying is entirely optional but available.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2967220/extras/Yan_Parasomnia_Toilet.gif?t=1720511283\" /><br><br><strong>Final Disclaimer</strong><br>The toilets do not contain any form of hidden treasures. <i>Maybe.</i>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2967220/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1720511283","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2967220/page.bg.jpg?t=1720511283","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2967220/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1720511283","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2967220/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1720511283","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Multi-player","id":1},{"description":"Co-op","id":9},{"description":"Online Co-op","id":38},{"de